B.Iu=s(["Working on Fundraising Project.","Implementing microservices & handling more than 10 services including :","{#}Storage Service, which manages asset storage.","{#}Internal Service for managing campaigns, beneficiaries, and validation processes carried out by administrators.","{#}Notification service, responsible for managing notifications such as push notifications, emails, and WhatsApp messages.","{#}Centralized configuration service.","{#}Referral service, allowing new users to connect by receiving certain benefits.","{#}Service for external partners. This service is provided for communication with partners.","{#}Service for managing Qurban.","{#}Monolithic service that is still running and used to this day.","{#}Interface service used by mobile apps & web apps. This service also implements user personalization and can be customized with user configuration.","{#}Regular donation service, donation streak, and donation reminder.","{#}Migrated a critical user-facing service (Home Page Engine) from Golang to Rust to enhance memory efficiency and landing page response time.","{#}Collaborated in a large-scale infrastructure migration from AWS to Google Cloud Platform (GCP).","{#}Led the database migration from PostgreSQL to MongoDB for managing user home page content and items.","{#}And others.","","I am accustomed to monitoring services using Grafana, creating alerts, and monitoring application usage (memory, CPU, and others). Most of the features I work on are based on research findings and input from application users. These research findings and user input are then managed together with the product team to be implemented into a feature."],t.s)
